        tempore fuga dolore earum eveniet vel voluptatum doloremque expedita!
        Deserunt, atque dolorem?
      </p>
      <h2>Wireframes</h2>
      <div class="mb-2 grid grid-cols-4 gap-2">
        <Image src={loginWireframe} alt="" class="border border-black" />
        <Image src={onboardingWireframe} alt="" class="border border-black" />
        <Image src={likesWirefrane} alt="" class="border border-black" />
        <Image src={eventsWireframe} alt="" class="border border-black" />
      </div>
      <figcaption class="mb-10 text-center text-sm">Wireframes</figcaption>
      <p>
        At this point, the user workflows were mostly mapped out and the app
        started to take shape. Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur
        adipisicing elit. Odio, mollitia? Eligendi, quis totam? Aperiam, id
        quam. Explicabo pariatur, tempore fuga dolore earum eveniet vel
        voluptatum doloremque expedita! Deserunt, atque dolorem?
      </p>
      <h2>V1 Designs</h2>
      <div class="mb-2 grid grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <Image src={loginV1} alt="" class="border border-black" />
        <Image src={onboardV1} alt="" class="border border-black" />
        <Image src={locationV1} alt="" class="border border-black" />
        <Image src={likesV1} alt="" class="border border-black" />
        <Image src={eventsV1} alt="" class="border border-black" />
        <Image src={accountV1} alt="" class="border border-black" />
      </div>
      <figcaption class="mb-10 text-center text-sm">V1 Designs</figcaption>
      <p>
        V1 designs. Early designs. Very short timeline. Needed to start
        development. Knew a future polished visual design was in the work.
        Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Odio,
        mollitia? Eligendi, quis totam? Aperiam, id quam. Explicabo pariatur,
        tempore fuga dolore earum eveniet vel voluptatum doloremque expedita!
        Deserunt, atque dolorem?
      </p>
      <h2>Workflows</h2>
      <div class="mb-2 grid grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <Image src={exploreV1} alt="" class="border border-black" />
        <Image src={exploreBioV1} alt="" class="border border-black" />
        <Image src={exploreEventsV1} alt="" class="border border-black" />
      </div>
      <figcaption class="mb-10 text-center text-sm">Explore Page</figcaption>
      <p>
        Main standout feature is the explore page. Most time spent there for an
        MVP. Idea is based on dating apps with swiping. Other areas are generic,
